{"Id":719028,"Title":"天净沙　塞上　八首","Dynasty":"清","Author":"屈大均","Context":"沙如乱雪非来。风吹忽作龙堆。塞水横冲不开。马蹄深陷，一鞭飞上平台。桑乾浊似黄河。冰开难饮明驼。滑滑春泥苦多。卤儿呼渡，雌雄两两吹螺。关门一线浮图。黄云半塞飞狐。雪尽莺花未藓，骆驼鞍暖，春宵卧过庐奴。千山已作边墙。长城更与天长。一望教人断肠。紫荆关外，茫茫只有牛羊。天寒雉兔偏多。挥鞭跃渡洋河。一箭双穿驾鹅。鱼鹰饥汝，鞍边割肉峨峨。天明已饭黄羊。笳声催上辞乡。泪落边因夕阳。蔚州煤好，春寒可代衣裳。盘山下见卢龙。三盘始上三峰。欲去依依暮钟。可怜明月，秋来之照边烽。居庸一口容人。开门谁揖黄巾。虎豹何曾苦辛。黑松林里，无劳间道通秦。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"天净沙","Status":2,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"4ec0dc0437f3565991ccf5cc4397b310","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":5785726,"Sentence":"雪尽莺花未藓，骆驼鞍暖，春宵卧过庐奴。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"xuě jin yīng huā wèi xiǎn ，jià tuó ān nuǎn ，chūn xiāo wò guō lú nú ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":10,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5785716,"Sentence":"沙如乱雪非来。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shā rú luàn xuě fēi lái ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5785717,"Sentence":"风吹忽作龙堆。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"fēng chuī hū zuō lóng duī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5785718,"Sentence":"塞水横冲不开。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"sāi shui héng chōng bú kāi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5785720,"Sentence":"桑乾浊似黄河。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"sāng gān zhuó shì huáng hé ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5785721,"Sentence":"冰开难饮明驼。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"bīng kāi nán yin mǐng tuó ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5785722,"Sentence":"滑滑春泥苦多。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"huá huá chūn nǐ kǔ duō ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5785724,"Sentence":"关门一线浮图。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"guān mén yī xiàn fú tú ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":8,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5785725,"Sentence":"黄云半塞飞狐。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"huáng yún bàn sāi fēi hú ","Tag":null,"Explanation"